  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Social Media Content Creator",
  "description": "<h3><strong>About Us</strong></h3><p>We are a dynamic and growing Chinese Restaurant Chain company looking to expand our online presence. Our mission is to engage audiences, build brand awareness, and create meaningful connections through digital platforms.</p><h3><strong>Responsibilities</strong></h3><p>Create, schedule, and publish engaging posts across social media platforms (Facebook, Instagram, LinkedIn, TikTok, Twitter, Youtube, Pintinterest, Telegram, Little Red Book, etc.).</p><p>Develop creative captions, hashtags, and visuals to maximize reach and engagement.</p><p>Monitor social media channels, respond to comments/messages, and foster community interaction.</p><p>Track performance metrics (likes, shares, impressions, click-throughs) and provide regular reports.</p><p>Stay updated on social media trends, tools, and best practices.</p><h3><strong>Requirements</strong></h3><p>Strong writing and communication skills with a flair for creativity.</p><p>Experience managing social media accounts (personal or professional).</p><p>Basic knowledge of design tools (Canva, Photoshop, or similar) is a plus.</p><p>Ability to work independently and meet deadlines.</p><p>Passion for digital marketing and storytelling.</p><h3><strong>Benefits</strong></h3><p>Opportunity to grow with a forward-thinking team.</p><p>Flexible working arrangements.</p><p>Exposure to diverse projects and creative freedom.</p>",
